*** Instalacion sublime text3 ***

Documentacion oficial : https://www.sublimetext.com/docs/linux_repositories.html

Instalacion : 
	
	wget -qO - https://download.sublimetext.com/sublimehq-pub.gpg | sudo apt-key add -
	sudo apt-get install apt-transport-https
	#Version stable : 
		echo "deb https://download.sublimetext.com/ apt/stable/" | sudo tee /etc/apt/sources.list.d/sublime-text.list
	sudo apt-get update
	sudo apt-get install sublime-text

Desistalacion :

	sudo apt-get remove --auto-remove sublime-text-installer
	sudo apt-get purge --auto-remove sublime-text-installer 
